<pb facs="1038341" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/>Viro Clarissimo et Doctissimo
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><salute><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>NB.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/>L<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tum accepi <rs key="B_991170517066305501" type="letter">nuntium</rs> à <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> mei Filio, <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person"/><note>Bernoulli, Nicolaus II (1695-1726)</note>, me tandem ab <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Excell.</abbr>
<lb/><abbr>Dnis</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089586140 pers_DE-588-1089586175 pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person"/><note type="editorial">Von 3.10.1716-4.11.1717 waren die Moderatoren der Universität Padua Michele Morosini di Lorenzo, Cavaliere (1670-1751), Francesco Soranzo (17./18. Jh.), Lorenzo Tiepolo (1673-1742)</note>Moderatoribus <rs type="organisation">Studii <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs></rs> electum esse in Professorem Mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>seos. Gaudeo felicem hujus negotii exitum unice deberi indefess<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>et incredibili studio, quo me <del> apud V</del><abbr>Excellmis</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089586140 pers_DE-588-1089586175 pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Proceribus <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetis</rs></rs>  co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endare
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tanto tempore nunquam destitisti. Primas igitur et maximas hanc ob
         <lb/>rem Tibi, ut <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quum est, ago gratias, rogans ut firmiter credas me si nulla
         <lb/>alia re, grato saltem animo beneficia Tua demeriturum esse. Inprimis
              <lb/>vero multum Tibi debeo quod vixdum recuperata valetudine <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>quam
         <lb/>morbo labefactam doluimus, nunc autem restitutam enixe Tibi gratulamur
             <lb/>ego et <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> meus<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> partes meas agere apud <abbr>Excellmos</abbr> <abbr>Dnos</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178380696 pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582" type="person">Reformatores</rs>
<lb/>iisdemque pro beneficio mihi collato meo nomine <add>debitas</add> gratias persolvere
         <lb/>constituisti, simulque curare ut liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> invitatori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quamprimum expediantur;
         <lb/>Spero id jam factum esse, easdemque literas propediem expecto, quibus accep<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis statim me ad discessum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>parabo, iterque ipsum post impetratam ab
             <lb/><abbr>Exc.</abbr> <rs type="organisation">Magistratu</rs> nostro <add>discedendi</add> veniam, aliaque negotia necessaria expedita aggre<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>diar. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum <del>confido</del> <add>ut </add>me <del> sub</del>iisdem conditionibus <subst><del>vocatum</del><add>astrictum</add></subst> iri, quibus
             <lb/>fuit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Herma<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>us</rs> noster, eodemque stipendio fruiturum confido, ita<del> spe</del> omni
             <lb/>vi ad id enitar, ut spei ab <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178380696 pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582" type="person">Reformatoribus</rs> de me concept<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
             <lb/>satisfaciam, gloriamque ac decus <rs type="organisation">ArchiLycei <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs></rs> <note type="editorial">Das L in Archilycei ist eine Majuskel, entsprechend der alten Schreibkonvention</note> in hoc saltem stu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dii genere, quod mihi profitendum erit, promoveam. Interim rogo me
         <lb/>moneas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> porro <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me fieri opus erit, et an, cui et quem in modum
         <lb/>post acceptas literas invitatorias mihi respondendum sit. Consilio
         <pb facs="1038342" n="2"/>
<lb/>Tuo et auxilio in omnibus utar, et quod scriptis nunc non possum, post
         <lb/>meum in vestras oras appulsum, quam vehementer me Tibi devinctum
              <lb/>agnoscam, Deo volente coram testabor.</p> <closer><salute>Vale</salute> et mihi ut facis porro fave.
          <lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, d. <date when="1716-06-06">6. <subst><del>Maji</del><add>Juni<unclear>i</unclear></add></subst> 1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript><p>
    <lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Gratias ago pro transmissa <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_P88RGPV8">solutione Problematis</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me propositi
    <lb/>quam <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1156361761" type="person">Sebastianus Checozzi</rs> Diario Veneto inseruit. Nisi <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_biblio_65T3BHVK">responsio</rs>
         <lb/>mea ultima jam, ut spero, impressa esset, monerem per additionem
         <lb/>aliquam hanc solutionem ex parte esse petitionem principii, facile
         <lb/>enim ostendere possem, <add><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1156361761" type="person">Checozzi</rs> tacite</add> supponere <del>illum tacite</del>curvam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sitam
         <lb/>fore unam ex parabolis, ex qua suppositione <add>ipsum postea</add> parabolam Cubicam
         <lb/>derivasse<del>pr<gap/><unclear>dum esse</unclear></del> non miror, sed miror quomodo ipsi i<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>otue<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rit hanc suppositionem faciendam esse.</p></postscript>
